                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.31">
                                <locus from="20r" to="25r" cert="low"/>
                                <title type="complete">Sǝbkat, Bǝrhān, Nolāwi, Lǝdāt, ʾAstarʾǝyo</title>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez"> ሰላም፡ ዘስብከት፡ ወዘብርሃን፡ ወዘኖላዊ፡ ወዘልደት፡ ወዘአስተርእዮ፡ ዘኲሎ፡ ድሙር፡  </incipit>
                                <note>The common salām for several festive periods: the Preaching, from the Sunday of the Preaching which is Sunday between <date> 8 Tāhśas </date> and <date> 14 Tāhśas </date> to the folllowing
                                Saturday; the Light, which is the collowing week; the Sheperd which is the following Sunday to <date> 27 Tāhśas</date>; the Nativity which is from <date> 29 Tāhśas </date>
                                    to <date> 10 Ṭǝrr</date>; the Epiphany, from <date> 10 Ṭǝrr</date> to the beginning of the Easter Cycle, qabalā.</note>
                            </msItem>

