                                <title type="complete">The Great Fast (<foreign xml:lang="gez">Ṣom</foreign>)</title>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez"> ሰላም፡ ዘጾም፡ ግዕዝ፡</incipit>
                                <note>Salām for the fasting time, the mode gǝʿz.</note>
                            </msItem>

                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.36">
                                <locus from="36r" cert="low"/>
                                <title type="complete"/>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez">ተሰቅለ፡ ወሐመ፡ በእንቲአነ፡ አኃውየ፡ የሀበነ፡ ሰላመ፡ ንግበር፡ በዓለ፡ ፋሲካ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡</incipit>
                                <note>Hymn for the passions and resurrection of Jesus Christ,
                                added in bleak ink.</note>
                            </msItem>
