           <div type="edition">
               <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="Takkaze" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/RNBdorn615#ms_i1.3">
                   <ab>
                    <pb n="3r"/>
                       በሰላም፡ ቦኡ፡ ሃገሮሙ፡ እለ፡ አሥመርዎ፡ ለእግዚኦሙ፡ በብዙኅ፡ ትፈሥሕት፡ ኀረዮሙ፡ ወባረኮሙ፡ እምኵሉ፡ አፈቀሮሙ፡ አዕይንተ፡ ተከዜ፡ አቀመ፡ ሎሙ፡ ለእለ፡
                       ይጸውሩ፡ ታቦተ፡ አምላከ፡ እስራኤል፡ ካህናት፨
                       አዕይንተ፡ ተከዜ፡ አቀምከ፡ ሎሙ፡ በኂሩትከ፡ ዐደዉ፡ ሰማዕት፡ ውስተ፡ ርስቶሙ፡ ጾሩ፡
                       ታቦቶሙ፡ እምፀሓይ፡ ይበርህ፡ ገጾሙ፡ በሰላም፡ ቦኡ፡ ሀገሮሙ፡ እንዘ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ምስሌሆሙ፡
                     </ab>
                    <listBibl type="translation">
                      <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/T6UTP6JE"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Turaev1906rukopisi"/><title level="m">Ėfiopskija rukopisi v S.-Peterburgě</title><title level="s">Pamjatniki ėfiopskoj pis'mennosti</title><author><forename>Boris</forename><surname>Turaev</surname></author><pubPlace>St Petersburg</pubPlace><publisher>Tipografija imperatorskoj Akademii Nauk</publisher><date>1906</date><series><title level="s">Pamjatniki ėfiopskoj pis'mennosti</title><biblScope unit="volume">3</biblScope></series><biblScope unit="volume">3</biblScope><note type="url">http://digitale-sammlungen.ulb.uni-bonn.de/content/titleinfo/2104581</note><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Manuscripts</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">bm:Turaev1906rukopisi</note></note><note type="tag">Manuscripts</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">bm:Turaev1906rukopisi</note><citedRange unit="page">16</citedRange></bibl>
                  </listBibl>

               </div>

               <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="Salāmā" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/RNBdorn615#ms_i1.29">
                   <ab>
                       <pb n="19r"/>
                       ዐዘቅተ፡ ክብር፡ ወትርሲተ፡ መንግሥት፡ ፈነወ፡ ወልዶ፡ ዘያፈቅር፡ አባ፡ ሰላማ፡ ገብረ፡ ሰላመ፡ ከሥተ፡ ብርሃነ፡ ወበምጽአቱ፡ ኪያነ፡ ቤዘወነ፡ እሉ፡ እሙንቱ፡ ዐዘቅተ፡ ጥበብ፡ እለ፡ ኮኑ፡
                       መምህራነ፡ ወሰበኩ፡ ለኵሉ፡ መጽአቱ፡ ለክርስቶስ፡ በሰላም፡ ወመሀሩ፡ በጽድቅ፡ ወበንጽሕ፡ ቃለ፡ እግዚአብሔር፨
                   </ab>

                   <listBibl type="translation">
                       <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/T6UTP6JE"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Turaev1906rukopisi"/><title level="m">Ėfiopskija rukopisi v S.-Peterburgě</title><title level="s">Pamjatniki ėfiopskoj pis'mennosti</title><author><forename>Boris</forename><surname>Turaev</surname></author><pubPlace>St Petersburg</pubPlace><publisher>Tipografija imperatorskoj Akademii Nauk</publisher><date>1906</date><series><title level="s">Pamjatniki ėfiopskoj pis'mennosti</title><biblScope unit="volume">3</biblScope></series><biblScope unit="volume">3</biblScope><note type="url">http://digitale-sammlungen.ulb.uni-bonn.de/content/titleinfo/2104581</note><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Manuscripts</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">bm:Turaev1906rukopisi</note></note><note type="tag">Manuscripts</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">bm:Turaev1906rukopisi</note><citedRange unit="page">16</citedRange></bibl>
                   </listBibl>

               </div>
               <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="Beginning" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/RNBdorn615#ms_i1.31">
                   <ab>
                       <pb n="20r"/>
                       ስብሐት፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ በሰማያት፡ ወሰላም፡ በምድር፡ ለዘሰበኩ፡ ነቢያት፡ ወከመ፡ ይመጽእ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ በስብሐት፡ ስብሐት፡ ለዘ፡ ቀደሳ፡ ለሰንበት።
                       <hi rend="rubric">ተሰብከ</hi>፡ በኦሪት፡ ዘመጽአ፡ ውስተ፡ ዓለም፡ ሰበክዎ፡ በአፈ፡ ነቢያት፡ እሙነ፡ ኮነ፡ በውስተ፡ ወንጌል፡ በሰላመ፡ ገብረ፡ ምጽአቱ፡ እምጥንቱ፡ እስከ፡ ተፍጻሜት።
                       ዜና፡ ንዜኑ፡ ለእለ፡ ይአምኑ፡ ዐቢየ፡ ፍሥሓ፡ ዘይከውን፡ ናሁ፡ ይመጽእ፡ እግዚእ፡ ወመድኅን፡ ዘያብርህ፡ ላዕለ፡ ጸድቃን፡ ወሀቤ፡ ሰላም፡ ዜናዊ፡ መምህረ፡ ቅዱሳን።
                       <hi rend="rubric">ንጉሥኪ</hi>፡ ጽዮን፡ በሰላም፡ ዘይዜኑ፡ ቃለ፡ ትፍሥሕት፡ ወሐሤት፡ በሰላም፡ ይዜኑ፡ አቅዲሙ፡ ሰበኩ፡ ነቢያት፡ በእንቲአሁ።
                       <hi rend="rubric">ፈነወ</hi>፡ ቃሎ፡ ለደቂቀ፡ እስራኤል፡ ወዜነዎሙ፡ ሰላመ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ዘውእቱ፡ እግዚእ፡ ለኵሉ፡ ወተሰብከ፡ ውስተ፡ ዓለም፡ ዜናሁ።
                   </ab>
